The three fixes that solve your specific issue of 58+ missing declarations are:

`_rewrite_with_declaration()` — called after every `copy_file()` for XML/rels files. This is the main fix for `copy13_colors1.xml`, `copy18_style2.xml` etc — they were being copied as raw bytes with no declaration ever added.

`_safe_write()` — used for every XML file your code generates directly (`numbering.xml`, `styles.xml`, `document.xml`, `[Content_Types].xml`, `.rels` files).

`_safe_copy()` — prevents namespace loss when cloning elements across documents.
